      "comment": "AUSSIE MIRAGE (8) was popular in betting last start but disappointed when 3.5 lengths away in fourth (26.45). Was in the money the start prior. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Key runner on his best form. MAXI GRIN (7) gave a start and copped a bump in running when finishing a 7 length sixth (26.75) at this track in a Maiden. Has the ability and can atone with the right run. WARATAH LAD (2) has his first outing without a trial but profiles nicely for this. Ratings suggest a place chance. WARATAH STORY (3) is by Aussie Infrared out of Waratah Miss making debut. Can sneak into the frame at her first appearance.",
